sentences: Marcus Schössow (Swedish pronunciation: [ˈmǎrːkɵs ˈɧœ̌sːɔv]; born (1985-10-28)October 28, 1985) is a Swedish DJ and producer.
He has also produced under the name Progresia, collaborated with Sebastian Brandt under the name Under Sun, and collaborated with Matthew Felner as gardenstate.
"Liceu", "Reverie" and "The Universe" (with Arston) are his major successes, reaching respectively the 8th, 11th, and 13th place in the top 100 downloads on Beatport.
He owns his recently established label Code Red Music.
Since its inception, four singles were released on the label, including "Generations" by the Dutch duo Magnificence.
